      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... they have their own lives. they have jobs and kids of their own. seeing them rush over here just to help me with things i used to do easily... it breaks my heart. it feels like I'm just an anchor dragging them down. i've always tried to be the one helping, not the one needing help. it feels wrong to keep going like this.",
